Title: Autoconfiscating Amd: Automatic Software Configuration of the Berkeley Automounter process of autoconfiscation, the pros of
Author: EREZ ZADOK 
Keyword: KEY WORDS Autoconf Automake Autoconfiscation Automounter Amd Libtool  
